episodes.title: Twin Flames Universe under investigation
episodes.description: We’re talking to a former member of the Twin Flames Universe about the State Attorney General’s investigation into its leaders.

episodes.title: Twin Flames Universe under investigation by Michigan attorney general, search warrants executed
episodes.description:
Michigan Attorney General Dana Nessel announced an ongoing investigation into Twin Flames Universe (TFU), which investigators say is being operated out of Leelanau County.

TFU is an organization with a largely online following operated by Jeff and Shaleia Divine and gained notoriety through a series of documentaries, AG Nessel said.

Special Agents from the Department of Attorney General, along with the U.S. Department of Labor-Office of Inspector General, and law enforcement officers from Michigan State Police, the Leelanau County Sheriff’s Office and the Grand Traverse County Sheriff’s Office executed search warrants Tuesday as a part of the investigation.

Read more: https://upnorthlive.com/news/local/twin-flames-universe-under-investigation-search-warrants-executed-in-leelanau-county#
